From 444259452fc65712d6233dc0bea248c55ac39325 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Hariharan Ramanathan <hramanat@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Tue, 10 Jun 2025 09:57:51 +0530
Subject: [PATCH 3/4] UPSTREAM CP DP: wifi: ath12k: Add telemetry stats for QCA
 Energy Service

Implement telemetry stats collection for QCA Energy Service:

Capture ath12k_pdev_telemetry_stats via WMI_CTRL_PATH_STATS_EVENTID
Capture ath12k_peer_telemetry_stats via HTT PPDU TX and PPDU DP MON path
Fetch these stats from the TLVs in each PPDU’s user info.
Add new members to existing data structures to store and update the
telemetry stats.

Patch-dependency: 982-01-QSDK-Infra-wifi-ath12k-Add-rm-file-to-Makefile.patch
Patch-work: None

Original Patch:
982-02-UPSTREAM-CP-DP-wifi-ath12k-Add-telemetry-stats-for-QCA-.patch

Signed-off-by: Sidhanta Sahu <quic_sidhanta@quicinc.com>
Signed-off-by: Hariharan Ramanathan <hramanat@qti.qualcomm.com>
